<subSubSection pageId="87" pageNumber="571" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="87.[137,1346,2728,3163]" pageId="87" pageNumber="571">
<taxonomicName authority="W. B. Davis &amp; D. C. Carter, 1964" authorityName="W. B. Davis &amp; D. C. Carter" authorityYear="1964" box="[139,385,2803,2836]" class="Mammalia" family="Phyllostomidae" genus="Artibeus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="87" pageNumber="571" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="inopinatus">Artibeus inopinatus</taxonomicName>
is in subgenus 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Leachi" authorityYear="1821" box="[603,709,2803,2836]" class="Mammalia" family="Phyllostomidae" genus="Artibeus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="87" pageNumber="571" phylum="Chordata" rank="genus">Artibeus</taxonomicName>
. Although usually considered closer to A. har sutus, molecular analyses suggested that 
<taxonomicName authority="W. B. Davis &amp; D. C. Carter, 1964" authorityName="W. B. Davis &amp; D. C. Carter" authorityYear="1964" box="[707,885,2842,2875]" class="Mammalia" family="Phyllostomidae" genus="Artibeus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="87" pageNumber="571" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="inopinatus">A. inopinatus</taxonomicName>
is sister to the clade A. harsutus + 
<taxonomicName authority="Anthony, 1924" authorityName="Anthony" authorityYear="1924" box="[139,313,2884,2917]" class="Mammalia" family="Phyllostomidae" genus="Artibeus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="87" pageNumber="571" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="fraterculus">A. fraterculus</taxonomicName>
. Monotypic.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection box="[139,1239,2921,2954]" pageId="87" pageNumber="571" type="distribution">
<caption ID-DOI="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6458973" ID-Zenodo-Dep="6458973" box="[139,1239,2921,2954]" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6458973/files/figure.png" inLine="true" pageId="87" pageNumber="571" targetBox="[1401,1992,285,698]" targetPageId="87">
<paragraph blockId="87.[137,1346,2728,3163]" box="[139,1239,2921,2954]" pageId="87" pageNumber="571">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[139,316,2921,2954]" pageId="87" pageNumber="571">Distribution.</emphasis>
