</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="87" pageNumber="571" type="conservation">
<paragraph blockId="87.[1405,2613,711,1332]" pageId="87" pageNumber="571">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1407,1756,1139,1172]" pageId="87" pageNumber="571">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
Classified as Data Deficient on The IUCN Red List. Additional information on population status and life history of the Honduran Fruit-eating Bat is needed to understand its conservation threats.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
